author: Matt Wixon
title: Super Boom: Twitter reaction to Frisco star lineman Jack Anderson committing to Tech
text:
Frisco's Jack Anderson, a junior who is rated by several recruiting services as the top center in the Class of 2017, announced that he has orally committed to Texas Tech:
